name: ˟_0xThxxghtx1˟perfectlyharmonizaedjazz...˟˟
description: Today I find myself quite inspired, to the sound of a perfectly harmonized jazz tone composed of dissonances, essentially chaos musically speaking, notes out of rhythm and humanized to the maximum, instruments that sound in unison as well, a set of chaotic elements in essence that generate a false sense of peace, but that in the background is chaos, and that I want to learn to assimilate as such, as a great chaos that makes me live, like water for the fish, a huge, uncontrollable and perfect chaos that reminds me and makes me clear that chaos is the false peace, is the false calm and that it is the true meaning of life, that there is nothing but chaos that gives me reasons to keep on living, writing this...
